{
  "texts": [
    "The comprehensive semantic information is obtained by quantum language-like of two adjacent content words.",
    "The proposed model linearly superimposes the adjacent word vectors through the tensor product to form a sentence representation and reduces the dimension of the sentence embedding from the sentence level and the correlated word level to mine more accurate semantics.",
    "Approaches An Attention Mechanism-Based Quantum-LikeSentence Embedding (AQE) Store WordInput each word from the sentence, eliminate any unrecognizable and high-frequency words, extract all content words, and store them orderly in an array A.A = {w 1, w 2, • • •, w n },(1)where n denotes the total number of the recognizable content words in the sentence.",
    "Match Word PairFor every word in the array A, pair it with its adjacent word to create word pairs, and store these pairs in an array B.B = {w 1 w 2, w 2 w 3, w 3 w 4, • • •, w n-1 w n }.",
    "(2)The PoSes of the two adjacent words are sequentially combined to form an array C, C = {P 1 P 2, P 2 P 3,P 3 P 4, • • •, P n-1 P n },(3)where P i denotes the PoS of the ith word."
  ]
}